<Layout
  title="Liebherr Appliance Repair | (424) 499-7788"
  description="Expert Liebherr appliance repair for refrigerators, freezers, wine refrigerators, built-in refrigeration, Monolith units, BioFresh systems, and NoFrost appliances. Professional Liebherr repair, maintenance, and installation support."
  ogImage="/liebherr/liebherr-refrigerator-repair.webp"
